high_descs: Pick up the pan from the stove.
Bring the pan to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge for 5 seconds then take it back out.
Bring the pan to the stove.
Put the pan down on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Cool the pan in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around to face the area to the left of the stove with a green garbage can.
Pick up the pan on the bottom left burner.
Turn around and position yourself in front of the fridge so you are facing it.
Chill the pan in the fridge for a bit before taking it back out and closing the fridge.
Go back to where you got the pan.
Put the pan back on the bottom left burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the stove top.

high_descs: Turn around and face the stove.
Turn around and hang right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the pan inside, and close it. Wait a moment, and take out the pan.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the pan on the front left burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan on a stove top.
